data.description: This gorgeous home 4 bedroom 2 1/2 bath is ready for you to move in! It is freshly painted with new landscaping. Upon entering the home, the office and dining room is to the left and the living room is straight ahead. The kitchen has beautiful granite countertops, dark cabinetry, and all Stainless appliances. The kitchen and breakfast areas are open to the living room for maximum entertainment opportunities. The primary bedroom has a large soaker tub and a separate shower.  Large upstairs game room and make sure to check out the huge backyard!
